Revision history for Perl module WWW::SMS::IE::iesms

3.18		2006-08-03

		Fixed bug introduced in previous release where logins weren't being re-used.

3.17		2006-08-01

		Added "--data-dir" option.

3.16		2006-07-25

		Added support for meteor's new site.

3.15		2006-07-18

		Actually fixed vodafone support.

3.14		2006-07-18

		Fixed vodafone support.
		
3.13		2006-06-12

		Fixed bug when using the '-c' option.
		Fixed bug with whitespace after config options.
		Fixed bug with erroneous cookie re-use.
		Fixed bug with specifying https_proxy on command line.

3.12		2006-05-25

		Fixed o2 support.
		Added '--history' feature.
		Warning if malformed configuration file.
		Fixed bug with incrementing counter in multi-part messages.
		Fixed bug with --no-reuse option not clearing cookie-jar.

3.11		2006-05-11

		Fixed bug with manual split not working on multi-lined messages.
		Improved startup time drastically.

3.10		2006-05-02

		Vodafone support.
		Fixed bug when specifying proxy.
		Allowing + style numbers on command line, improving invalid number check.
		Improved Win32 compatibility.
		Command line arguments now override config file settings.

3.09		2006-03-20

		Using international number format.
		Clearing cookie jar before login.
		Moved carrier specific processing into sub-modules.
		Fixed bug when saving already-existing aliases.
		Fixed bug when specifying message on command line.
		Fixed bug with processing '--' arguments.

3.08		2006-03-08

		Minimum required for URI module is version 1.26.
		Workaround for bug in LWP::UserAgent using HTTPS proxies.
		-version

3.07		2006-03-03

		Fixed bug introduced by 3.06.

3.06		2006-03-03

		Bug fix in v2 -> v3 migration.

3.05		2006-03-02

		Improved auto-aliasing. Config file documentation.

3.04		2006-02-28

		Small bug fixes

3.03		2006-02-28

		Small bug fixes

3.00		2006-02-27

		First CPAN release.

